                    <!-- CONVERT TO MSPART and list all items. -->
                    <head>Fourteen documents, mostly Persian, including several presented to Colonel
                        George William Hamilton upon his appointment as Commissioner of Delhi in
                            <date calendar="#Gregorian" when="1862">1862</date> and thereafter.</head>
                    <msContents>

                        <summary>This collection contains several panegyric poems and ornate prose
                            compositions dated to the mid-19th century.</summary>
